The source code in this repository does not include the LOINC dataset; users
must download LOINC themselves from https://loinc.org/downloads/ and accept the
LOINC license before running this software. The dataset is loaded into a local
Postgres database via the import script in scripts/import-loinc.ts.

When this software is deployed and surfaces LOINC content (codes, names,
synonyms, etc.), the deployment retains LOINC's required attribution. The
running site reproduces the notice below at /about, linked from the footer.

